OL,3,CTop 20 world's happiest countries
OL,4,Crevealed - where does the UK rank?
OL,6,FThe report - published on the United
OL,7,FNations International Day of Happiness
OL,8,FMarch 20 - asks each participant to
OL,9,Fscore their life as a whole, looking
OL,10,Fat six key variables to help explain
OL,11,Flife evaluations: GDP per capita,
OL,12,Fsocial support, healthy life
OL,13,Fexpectancy, freedom, generosity and
OL,14,Fperceptions of corruption.
OL,16,FFinland and its Nordic neighbours -
OL,17,FDenmark, Iceland and Norway - all
OL,18,Fstormed the top ten.
