OL,6,FBut there is a possibly surprising
OL,7,Fappearance from Israel at number five,
OL,8,Falthough the country has been in the
OL,9,Ftop ten since 2022.
OL,11,FThe authors point out that its
OL,12,Frankings are based on a three-year
OL,13,Faverage, which often dampens the
OL,14,Feffect of "cataclysmic events
OL,15,Fhappening during a particular year."
